{
  "stem": "11611.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I went to [NON-ENGLISH] and talked to the Philips officials, Philips being a big radio communications firm, who were suspected of collaborating with the Germans anyhow.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I talked to various people in Holland and Belgium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to Paris fairly often, but that was not on business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Maybe every two months I'd go there because my sister was going to school there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She was at the Sorbonne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And similarly, at a couple points I went to London because she had moved from the Sorbonne to Oxford.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So those were kind of five-day vacations which I would periodically take.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But Prague was a mix in the course of business and sometimes just a few days off because you get there quickly.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A year.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A year.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not only the bank case, all the cases.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had the Reichsbank, the German Ministry of Economics, which-- the Dresdner Bank was closely tied to my ministry of economics defendant.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They did business together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when necessary, they would invoke the services of the Gestapo or the SD.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were very helpful in negotiating with people who were not friendly to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The SD was a kind of a police branch of the SS, literally translated in German as Sicherheitsdienst, which means security service of the SS.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS itself was called the Schutzstaffel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what the SS comes from, and that means the defense group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a party group, and came into existence before the Nazis seized political power.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, it was a selected bunch of thugs, and of those thugs, the SD was even more thuggish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The SD was probably a little bit worse than the Gestapo, whose reputation is well founded.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll give you a concrete illustration.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
